textAfterTable: 10 Songs Biography Genre: Salsa and Tropical Years Active: '60s, '70s, '80s, '90s, '00s, '10s Led by pianist and musical director Rafael Ithier (born: Rafael Ithier Eddie Perez), El Gran Combo de Puerto Rico is one of Puerto Rico's greatest dance bands. Four decades after their inception, the 13-piece salsa group continues to inspire dancers with its horn-punctuated Latin rhythms and lush vocal harmonies.
